
This website uses the Confeature framework:
	http://github.com/Skreo/confeature
You should rename the ISEPLive's root dir "app" and put it in the same dir than Confeature's dir.

INSTALL FROM THE GIT REPO
=========================

mkdir iseplive
cd iseplive

# Confeature dir
git clone git://github.com/Godefroy/confeature.git confeature

# App dir
wget --no-check-certificate https://github.com/Godefroy/iseplive/tarball/master -O app.tar.gz
tar -xf app.tar.gz
rm app.tar.gz
mv *-iseplive-* app

# Data dir
mkdir -p data/logs
mkdir -p data/tmp


Quick deployment
----------------

project/app/cli/export.sh


Dependencies
------------

Required packages :
	apache2
	php5
	php5-gd
	php5-ldap
	php5-memcache
	php-apc
	php5-ffmpeg
	ffmpeg
	memmcached
	mysql-server
	
Required Apache mods:
	rewrite
	deflate
	headers
	expires

PHP config:
	upload_max_filesize = 700M
	post_max_size = 700M

ElasticSearch:
	The last stable release is here: http://www.elasticsearch.com/download/
	
	wget --no-check-certificate http://github.com/downloads/elasticsearch/elasticsearch/elasticsearch-0.13.1.tar.gz
	tar -xf elasticsearch-*.tar.gz
	cd elasticsearch-*
	wget --no-check-certificate https://github.com/elasticsearch/elasticsearch-servicewrapper/tarball/master
	tar -xf elasticsearch-elasticsearch-servicewrapper-*.tar.gz
	rm elasticsearch-elasticsearch-servicewrapper-*.tar.gz
	mv elasticsearch-elasticsearch-servicewrapper-*/service ./bin/
	rm -r elasticsearch-elasticsearch-servicewrapper-*
	bin/service/elasticsearch install
	/etc/init.d/elasticsearch start
